Glad to see this come back to life. Thanks for comments all.

@dsm054 is absolutely correct that the new tests for ranking methods (other than dense ranking) are testing the expected results given the existing code. I am not sure what the correct results are for each ranking method, but I wanted to make sure we have tests for when we fix the ranking methods. 

If you can help me determine the correct results for each ranking method, then I can update the pull request, or we can close as is and fix in a separate pull request.

@gfyoung: I'm happy to add jreback's whatsnew suggestion. Will update soon.
